Program: Outlook
Title: HIV/Aids in China
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs23
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
One man's story of living with Aids in China. Also, an eyewitness account of a violent incident in Ghana and how it changed his life. Grumpy civil servants in Egypt. Aids in Kenyan universities. Rival claims on ownership of the Siachen Glacier. Gidon Bromberg on trying to clean up the River Jordan. Finally, the great-grandmother who had a living will tattooed on her body. Show less